{"tid":1012461,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[長沙灣流浪貓][成功收編] 今日成功捉到隻勁瘦既流浪貓咪","createTime":"2019-02-07T15:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T15:48:44.000Z","uid":234540,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fc26072cc16d4c1daee62b6617ed1cbc4e31e4","tid":1012461,"uid":234540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早兩個禮拜開始係長沙灣見到隻勁瘦又嗲人既貓咪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230152_8faf81d9437b3ecd859327f38132e0f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230152_8faf81d9437b3ecd859327f38132e0f8.png&h=083c1119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時同隻貓玩既同時吸引左好多人圍觀，加入一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後來有幾位暖男買小食買罐罐比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230352_1ef1224eb557578341a37ac858ece47c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230352_1ef1224eb557578341a37ac858ece47c.png&h=6f04b9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230354_3b733c524b66c70e73e160b344760bc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230354_3b733c524b66c70e73e160b344760bc0.png&h=da47118a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住連續幾日大家都一齊幫手餵貓貓，又商量捉佢收編<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋日我有朋友見到隻貓好鐘意，話想收編<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，今日成功捉到啦，輕鬆！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230632_fbc8b57c850aff68aaff45770a398ba9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230632_fbc8b57c850aff68aaff45770a398ba9.png&h=2b3ba4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230634_bcc1d4e0e1f070d2f6822e24960a43fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230634_bcc1d4e0e1f070d2f6822e24960a43fb.png&h=bcb6cf55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230636_68b70a3604ae9e53f28d5be8c7f07839.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230636_68b70a3604ae9e53f28d5be8c7f07839.png&h=07c50d96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/230637_c3bc87167068d0f7d4f80d77e401a853.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F230637_c3bc87167068d0f7d4f80d77e401a853.png&h=2342e533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前新貓困住籠等佢熟識下環境先，好彩新貓都算定，又肯食野，無乜喵喵叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過朋友果邊有另一隻貓，一見到主人收編埋另一隻貓就好似有啲敵意，又發脾氣。點搞好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7ca5a55a424af64df7a84652c896f9caf8323c","tid":1012461,"uid":14094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"帶去獸醫望望有冇病先啦"},{"pid":"aac5e85001f67c720bb49f62ecd5447a2cc686be","tid":1012461,"uid":234540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b7ca5a55a424af64df7a84652c896f9caf8323c","tid":1012461,"uid":14094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"帶去獸醫望望有冇病先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"諗住過兩日先帶佢去睇，新年啲獸醫未開工，同埋想佢情緒定少少先"},{"pid":"2016afdddfd3cc27c01388501f51c7efeafdaa90","tid":1012461,"uid":14094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"aa